  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Restaurants &amp; Bars</strong></span></p>
<p>Kabuga Restaurant is open for breakfast, lunch and dinner offering a traditional Sardinian dishes using local produce.<br />Lucina Pizzeria offers a casual lunch spot for wood-fired pizzas.</p>
<p>Pool Grill serves international dishes next to the pool including grilled vegetables with freshly-caught fish and delicious hamburgers, as well as a range of refreshing cocktails.</p>
<p>Le Due Lanterne Terrace has a panoramic terrace overlooking the harbour, where you can sit back with a glass of prosecco and an aperitif.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Swimming pool</li>
<li>Solarium</li>
<li>Wellness centre</li>
<li>Small gym</li>
<li>Boat rental</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
