  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>Rooms range from simple Sardinian boltholes to luxury suites. They all have air-conditioning, soundproofed windows, hairdryers, satellite TVs, phones, Wi-Fi, minibars, electronic safes and room service.</p>
<p><strong>Comfort Rooms</strong> look over the hills or garden. Some have a small furnished terrace.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> have a balcony with marina views.</p>
<p><strong>Spacious Junior Suites</strong> also offer a sea-view balcony. Suites add a living room with an extra terrace or balcony. They also have tea-making stations with a kettle and teapot. These rooms are available on request, Please call to book </p>]]></roomsDescription>
